e portal fragment it costs to translocate you, but I do ask that you carry them.  It wouldn't be so bad if these were on most merchants like food and water are, but it's sold by a single person and requires you to navigate the better part of 3 zones to get to and, in reality, I'm too lazy to make that trip 2 or 3 times a week to offer ports to strangers. <br><br>While were on the subject of ports, I'll go ahead and list a few of my personal pet peeves about port requests. <br><br><ol><li><b>Anonymous people sending me blind tells for ports.</b> You used the /who system to find me and expect me to be available to service you, but you don't want to extend the same courtesy? No thanks.  <li><b>Asking me to leave my group.</b> Sorry, I feel this is rude.  If I am in a group, you are out of luck unless I am the leader and there's an open spot ... I refuse to interrupt my group simply because you think you are entitled to a port.<li><b>Asking me to rebind to make your port request possible.</b> Whether it be that you want to go to EJ, SF, or S. Ro (the places you can't Translocate to) or you want me to port to you so you have transportation, don't ask me to rebind.  You might as well just send me a tell saying, "Would you be so kind as to put me on your 'never port again' list?"<li><b>Asking me to come to you.</b> I generally port people without asking for compensation, I feel I am doing you a favor. If you feel the same way, you could at least come to me. <br></ol> <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=5072">Traven</a><br>Sorcerer of <a href="http://www.guildvision.org/">Vision</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/umysthawk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mysthawk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Been around a while</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/31/02 12:56:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAd